{"tid":731381,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[耳機撚] 討論各大耳機店及耳機(64)","createTime":"2018-07-06T06:35:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T14:58:29.000Z","uid":101600,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8bb471c2f9348c428fd7a0adc1e68ab4ff2d0ab2","tid":731381,"uid":101600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T06:35:35.000Z","msg":"Copy from 夜夜夜<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">各位新黎既巴絲請詳細閱讀第一頁，以免問題不停回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><br />\n所有耳機/player/線一切以你自己對耳為標準<br />\n<br />\n耳機聽感自己試<br />\n啱唔啱聽自己知<br />\n-punk巴<br />\n<br />\n所有野信自己對耳好過信sales / post內巴打<br />\n巴打/sales對耳仔唔係你對耳仔 每個人聽感都唔同<br />\n買野前一定要自己試清楚諗清楚<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新黎既巴/絲打歡迎留一留低自己聽歌器材既資料(新link)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/viewform?formkey=dFFGTFdGV21nemQteldTaV83V1lKSlE6MQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheet%2Fviewform%3Fformkey%3DdFFGTFdGV21nemQteldTaV83V1lKSlE6MQ&d=GPWZBtuTsridr%2BxWHMGzFf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=6a393691\" target=\"_blank\">http://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/viewform?formkey=dFFGTFdGV21nemQteldTaV83V1lKSlE6MQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢頁可以睇番其他巴打填左乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/ccc?key=0AsCwmQJKoVjPdFFGTFdGV21nemQteldTaV83V1lKSlE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheet%2Fccc%3Fkey%3D0AsCwmQJKoVjPdFFGTFdGV21nemQteldTaV83V1lKSlE&d=GPWZBtuTsridr%2BxWHMGzFf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=1eade198\" target=\"_blank\">http://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/ccc?key=0AsCwmQJKoVjPdFFGTFdGV21nemQteldTaV83V1lKSlE</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n舊Link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:<br />\n<a href=\"http://tinyurl.com/eargay2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftinyurl.com%2Feargay2&d=GPWZBtuTsridr%2BxWHMGzFf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=9cf2d4f9\" target=\"_blank\">http://tinyurl.com/eargay2</a><br />\n<br />\n耳機潮文合集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:<br />\n  <a href=\"http://docs.google.com/document/d/1Im5370mKsPKPZGJhqVGWocLcy5P22YHgdlnx5hmlx_k/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1Im5370mKsPKPZGJhqVGWocLcy5P22YHgdlnx5hmlx_k%2Fedit&d=GPWZBtuTsridr%2BxWHMGzFf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=941609eb\" target=\"_blank\">http://docs.google.com/document/d/1Im5370mKsPKPZGJhqVGWocLcy5P22YHgdlnx5hmlx_k/edit</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n經典耳機推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://docs.google.com/document/d/1tMEkzWyPyuTw56QVJNdV8TIRk30M3w03RN4xEYWLkD8/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1tMEkzWyPyuTw56QVJNdV8TIRk30M3w03RN4xEYWLkD8%2Fedit&d=GPWZBtuTsridr%2BxWHMGzFf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=6e6b5a40\" target=\"_blank\">http://docs.google.com/document/d/1tMEkzWyPyuTw56QVJNdV8TIRk30M3w03RN4xEYWLkD8/edit</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCM推介(舊link唔見埋, 可能有漏<br />\n<a href=\"http://docs.google.com/document/d/1FKYVT8FxSpocfPju5aFfPVWAUbryrv-eVKBRvItYKLM/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1FKYVT8FxSpocfPju5aFfPVWAUbryrv-eVKBRvItYKLM%2Fedit&d=GPWZBtuTsridr%2BxWHMGzFf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=985bba6a\" target=\"_blank\">http://docs.google.com/document/d/1FKYVT8FxSpocfPju5aFfPVWAUbryrv-eVKBRvItYKLM/edit</a><br />\n香港常見既既CM有:<br />\nfitear 333, 334, 335, air, aya<br />\nVE5, 6XC, 8<br />\n64 a18 (遲d有a12t) <br />\nqdc 變色龍,qdc 8, 雙子<br />\nUERR, 18pro<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAmp推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://docs.google.com/document/d/17OY_8Vrf3tGrWj-sbKXFbKiMDmFgL6r-UFt4XQVCqUc/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F17OY_8Vrf3tGrWj-sbKXFbKiMDmFgL6r-UFt4XQVCqUc%2Fedit&d=GPWZBtuTsridr%2BxWHMGzFf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=44f753eb\" target=\"_blank\">http://docs.google.com/document/d/17OY_8Vrf3tGrWj-sbKXFbKiMDmFgL6r-UFt4XQVCqUc/edit</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDIY AMP<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://docs.google.com/document/d/1bPwtk_hct0uIywm4Ty1ykZzxuUdOpZNygMHtIVQ6T7M/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1bPwtk_hct0uIywm4Ty1ykZzxuUdOpZNygMHtIVQ6T7M%2Fedit&d=GPWZBtuTsridr%2BxWHMGzFf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=06c72fd5\" target=\"_blank\">http://docs.google.com/document/d/1bPwtk_hct0uIywm4Ty1ykZzxuUdOpZNygMHtIVQ6T7M/edit</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"fbfed2dde98c229ec6c8cc002d5cee699be6bf70","tid":731381,"uid":101600,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T06:36:24.000Z","msg":"有冇人知點解得𣾀豐/恆生有得做分期<br />\n其他銀行又冇?"},{"pid":"708bd90b1cd8d9c67820fa622e99e138c34881bb","tid":731381,"uid":39536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T07:10:09.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"b68635cb7848f64cf551990f2be33e564c545fec","tid":731381,"uid":151927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T07:50:56.000Z","msg":"Lm學野"},{"pid":"30deb488d8ff3577e7c3fe383001a427678297d4","tid":731381,"uid":147057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T07:54:57.000Z","msg":"新po留名"},{"pid":"c53e27709a39de9db95bd239632d4d491c12db9f","tid":731381,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbfed2dde98c229ec6c8cc002d5cee699be6bf70","tid":731381,"uid":101600,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T06:36:24.000Z","msg":"有冇人知點解得𣾀豐/恆生有得做分期<br />\n其他銀行又冇?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T08:02:58.000Z","msg